html:
name

The name of the element to which the new element is connected. Creatio will use this name to locate the elements in the replaced schemas and to connect the elements with the new element. The name property of the diff revision array element cannot equal the alias.name property.

excludeProperties

An property array of the values ​​object of the element from the diff modification array. The properties will not be applied when building diff.

excludeOperations

An array of operations that must not be applied to this element when building the diff array of modifications.
